**			      1101 to 1102 - run iixprocedure tests 1 and 2
**			OPT:    101 to 105 - run iistatistics tests 1 to 5
**			        201 to 202 - run iihistogram tests 1 to 2
**			IIDBDB: 101 to 102 - run iicdbid_idx tests 1 to 2
